metadata.name: REACHING
metadata.description:
We're all reaching for something, whether it's love, recognition, success, help, or hope. We're all craving change.

" REACHING"  is the beginning a collective experience to discover the possibilities of our space, enjoy art, push the limits and have a lot fun. Get an edition and join the experience.  keep reaching for the stars.

20% of the proceeds will  be reinvested into the community buying art from artists.  
From Beeartem  
2960 x 4000px
